arts.sum: The Saddlers come into this match having lost just one of their last thirteen games and have won five of their last seven, victory for the Saddlers would see them go four points clear of the promotion...

arts.ttl: The Baggie raised by a Blue & from warehouse work to Walsall | EFL short stories
arts.sum: With 18 EFL games live on Sky Sports+ on Tuesday night, we take a look at some of the stories with six players from the Championship, League One and League Two.

arts.ttl: AFC Wimbledon boss bemused after being denied penalty shout during Walsall loss
arts.sum: “It’s a penalty, he gets pushed in the back in the box,” said Jackson. I don’t want to be a fussy team but we’ve got to look at that because we’re getting penalty shouts turned down all the time.”
